「'''年齡驗證'''」（'''Age Verification'''），是一項社交功能，其允許用戶透過第三方服務 [https://withpersona.com/ Persona] 驗證年齡。已驗證的用戶可在其個人檔案上顯示年齡驗證標記，並得以加入具年齡限制的[[Special:MyLanguage/Instances|房間（Instances）]]。此功能於 2024 年 11 月 27 日，在 VRChat 官方 YouTube 頻道上正式公布。<ref name=":0">VRChat 發布在 YouTube 上的 [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=odiNjIFUNvw Introducing Age Verification | Developer Update #vrchat]。發布於 [2024-11-27]。存取於 [2024-11-27]。</ref>

截至 2025 年 1 月 28 日，驗證流程目前仍以搶先體驗的形式開放給所有 [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] 訂閱用戶使用。<ref>VRChat 發布在 Bluesky 上的 [https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com/post/3lgtoi5ho2227 Age Verification is now available for VRC+ Subscribers!...]，發布於 [2025-01-28]。</ref>

<span id="Process"></span>
==流程==

年齡驗證流程主要透過第三方平台 [https://withpersona.com/ Persona] 服務進行。用戶需提供所在國政府身分證件<ref>[https://docs.withpersona.com/reference/government-id-verifications 政府核發的身分證件驗證（Government ID Verifications）]，位於 ''withpersona.com''。存取於 [2024-12-09]。</ref>，並使用具備攝影功能的裝置，例如智慧型手機或配備網路攝影機的電腦，才能夠完成驗證。

幾乎任何形式的政府核發身分證件皆可使用，但可使用的類型會依用戶所在國家而有所不同，例如：具備 NFC 功能的護照（或電子護照）。

用戶可透過此[https://vrchat.com/home/ageverification 連結]，在 VRChat 官方網站上進行年齡驗證。 

''Persona 會依照其隱私政策<ref>Persona 發布的[https://withpersona.com/legal/privacy-policy 隱私政策（Privacy Policy）]。存取於 [2024-11-27]。</ref>處理用戶的身分證件資料與生物辨識資料，並確保其符合[[wikipedia:General_Data_Protection_Regulation|《一般資料保護規則》（GDPR）]]、[[wikipedia:California_Consumer_Privacy_Act|《加州消費者隱私法》（CCPA）]]以及其他相關合規標準<ref>Persona 發布的[https://withpersona.com/security 保障說明]。存取於 [2024-11-28]。</ref>。VRChat 不會接收或儲存驗證流程中的個人資訊，唯一例外是用戶經驗證後的出生日期。Persona 與 VRChat 之間採用資料處理協議（Data Processing Agreement，DPA），該協議要求 Persona 對所有用戶皆須依照《一般資料保護規則》、《加州消費者隱私法》標準運作，而不受所在地區限制<ref>Tupper 發布在 VRChat Forum 上的[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/age-verification-faq/28458#p-58953-what-if-i-dont-live-in-the-eu-or-california-10 年齡驗證 Q&A（Age Verification FAQ）]。發布於 [2024-12-02]。存取於 [2024-12-09]。</ref>。''

<span id="Features"></span>
== 功能 ==

<span id="Profile_marker"></span>
===個人檔案標記===

[[File:Age verif Update Status.webp|thumb|個人檔案中切換顯示「'''已確認年滿 18 歲'''」（'''Verified 18+'''）之處。|200x200px]]

已完成年齡驗證且年滿 18 歲的用戶，可選擇在其個人資料上顯示標記，以表示其 18+ 年齡驗證狀態。
*「'''已確認年滿 18 歲'''」（'''Verified 18+'''）之選項，僅可由已完成年齡驗證，且已年滿 18 歲的用戶使用。
若用戶不希望讓其他人看見其驗證狀態，也可選擇完全隱藏該標記。已驗證為 18+ 的用戶，無論其個人檔案上是否公開顯示驗證標記，皆可存取有開設年齡限制的房間。

僅有年齡驗證的信任盾牌圖示本身「'''並不代表'''」該用戶已年滿 18 歲，它僅代表該用戶已完成年齡驗證。年滿 13 歲而未滿 18 歲的用戶，也可以透過 Persona 完成年齡驗證，但在年滿 18 歲之前，將無法在其個人資料上選擇「'''已確認年滿 18 歲'''」標記，也無法存取有年齡限制的房間。

<span id="Age_gated_instances"></span>
====年齡限制房間====


[[File:AgeRestrictedInstance.webp|alt=A screenshot of a group public instance in a world's instances list. An icon resembling an ID card with a checkmark on it indicating it is an age-restricted instance.|thumb|199x199px|有年齡限制的房間會在房間資訊中以「身分證」圖示作為標示。]]

[[Special:MyLanguage/Groups|群組（Groups）]]可以建立 18 歲年齡限制的[[Special:MyLanguage/Instances|房間]]，其要求所有參與者必須已完成年齡驗證，且年滿 18 歲才能加入。此限制可套用至「公開」、「群組 +」、「群組」房間。若用戶已完成 18 歲驗證，則年齡限制房間將始終顯示在房間列表的最上方。

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Content Gating===
</div>


{{noticebox/unreleased|{{Upcoming_inline|H1 2026|hello.vrchat.com/blog/trust-safety-update-2025}}}}

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
''Age Verification is to function alongside [[Special:MyLanguage/Content_Gating|Content Gating]] to prevent unverified users and verified users under the age of 18 from accessing content tagged with "Sexually suggestive" and "Adult language and themes". This is expected to take place in the first half of 2026.<ref>VRChat (2025, December 19). ''Safety, Freedom, and the Future of VRChat''. Retrieved December 20, 2025, from https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/trust-safety-update-2025</ref><ref>Tupper (2024, December 3). ''Age Verification FAQ''. VRChat Forum. Retrieved December 9, 2024, from https://ask.vrchat.com/t/age-verification-faq/28458#p-58953-what-other-content-or-systems-will-be-affected-by-age-verification-37</ref>.''
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Rollout==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The feature was originally limited to select groups during a trial period, where only members of selected groups could apply for verification slots and create age-restricted instances<ref name=":0" />.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The first rollout begun December 17th, 2024, multiple selected groups were given access to age verification for group users. <!-- do we know how many? -->
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
On January 28th, 2025 the feature was rolled out to all [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat+|VRC+]] subscribers as an Early Access feature. There is currently no confirmed date as to when it will become available to all users.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Additional information==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
*'''Verification Requirements:''' Users must submit an ''unedited'' photo of their government ID for it to be accepted as well as complete a "liveliness check" involving a selfie to ensure the person validating is the same as the person who owns the ID<ref>Tupper (2024, December 2). ''Age Verification FAQ''. VRChat Forum. Retrieved December 9, 2024, from https://ask.vrchat.com/t/age-verification-faq/28458#p-58953-what-do-i-need-to-submit-to-verify-my-age-4</ref>.
*'''Optional:''' Age verification is not mandatory to use VRChat. However, to be able to access age-restricted instances and features a user must verify their age ''and'' be 18 or older<ref>Tupper (2024, December 2). ''Age Verification FAQ''. VRChat Forum. Retrieved December 9, 2024, from https://ask.vrchat.com/t/age-verification-faq/28458#p-58953-is-age-verification-mandatory-6</ref>.
*'''Data Handling:''' ID data is retained by Persona for the minimum amount of time it takes to verify the user's birthdate and to create a unique one-way [[wikipedia:Cryptographic_hash_function|cryptographic hash]] utilizing data from the user's provided ID. This hash is stored on VRChat's servers for that user's account and all ID data is deleted on Persona's end, the irreversible cryptographic hash and user's verified Date of Birth remain on VRChat's servers.<ref>https://youtu.be/lzG9IwmM7TI</ref>
**'''Note:''' Deleting verification data in VRChat will result in the user's account being unusable until they accept the Terms of Service and input their birthdate again. This will also result in verification status being removed from that account unless it is reverified.
*'''One ID Per Account:''' One ID cannot be used to verify multiple accounts. This restriction is intended to enhance trust, and encourage users to place more value in their account, discouraging malicious behavior<ref>Tupper (2024, December 2). ''Age Verification FAQ''. VRChat Forum. Retrieved December 9, 2024, from https://ask.vrchat.com/t/age-verification-faq/28458#p-58953-can-i-use-the-same-id-to-verify-multiple-accounts-8</ref>.
*'''18+ ≠ Sexually Explicit Content:''' 18+ Age verification or age-restricted instances do ''not'' waive the [[Special:MyLanguage/Terms of Service|Terms of Service]] or [[Special:MyLanguage/Community Guidelines|Community Guidelines]] policy on pornographic content.
**Refer to section 13.2 of the [https://hello.vrchat.com/legal Terms of Service]<ref>VRChat (2024, November 18). ''VRChat Terms of Service''. Retrieved December 9, 2024, from https://hello.vrchat.com/legal#:~:text=13.2.%20Prohibited%20Conduct</ref> as well as the [https://hello.vrchat.com/community-guidelines Community Guidelines]<ref>VRChat (2024, August 12). ''VRChat Community Guidelines''. Retrieved December 9, 2024, from https://hello.vrchat.com/community-guidelines</ref>.
</div>

